---
title: Speedy Creamy Chorizo and Sweetcorn Pasta with Diced Chicken Breast with Spinach and Cheese
description: This Speedy Creamy Chorizo and Sweetcorn Pasta with Diced Chicken Breast is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
